d 'THESIS_DIAGRAM': module to generate LaTeX code for thesis framework diagrams with 5 templates
d
d    thesis_diagram generates professional LaTeX code for thesis
d and dissertation framework diagrams. It    supports 5 different
d templates suitable for various research designs and
d methodologies. The program	creates a standalone LaTeX file
d that can be compiled to produce high-quality vector graphics for 
d   academic publications. 
d
d KW: document
d KW: LaTeX
d KW: thesis
d KW: dissertation
d
d Requires: Stata version 16
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260209
d
d Author: Wu LiangHai,  Anhui University of Technology
d Support: email agd2010@@yeah.net
d
d Author:   Wu Hanyan, Nanjing University of Aeronautics and Astronautics
d Support: email    2325476320@@qq.com
d
d Author:   Jin Xuening,  Anhui University of Technology
d Support: email     1418924481@@qq.com
d
f thesis_diagram.ado
f thesis_diagram.sthlp
